{# Services #}
<section class="relative isolate overflow-hidden px-6 py-24 sm:py-32 lg:px-8">
	<div class="mx-auto prose prose-2xl max-w-4xl">
		<h2 id="custom-software" class="font-medium uppercase" style="text-wrap: balance">Crafted Software Solutions
			<span class="text-xl block text-brand-red-700">Tailored for Your Business</span></h2>
		<div class="border-t-2">
			<p>When your business has outgrown spreadsheets, disconnected tools, and manual workarounds, off-the-shelf software can start creating as many problems as it solves. I help small and medium-sized organizations turn those messy workflows into focused web applications that fit how the team actually works.</p>
			<p>That might mean a customer portal, an internal dashboard, a reporting workflow, or an AI-assisted tool that helps people search, summarize, classify, or act on information faster. The work starts with the business problem, then uses the right mix of software, automation, and AI to make the process clearer and easier to run.</p>
			<h3>Where AI can help</h3>
			<p>AI is most useful when it is attached to a real workflow: reviewing documents, finding answers across internal knowledge, cleaning up messy data, drafting routine responses, or spotting patterns your team already knows to look for. I help identify the places where it earns its keep, then build it into the tools your team already uses.</p>
			<p class="">
				<a href="#contact" class="bg-brand-red-700 px-3.5 py-2.5 text-white shadow-sm no-underline hover:bg-brand-red-800 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-brand-red-600">Let's talk!</a>
			</p>

		</div>
	</div>
</section>

